      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that slips between gears. The exterior has noticeable body damage, including rust spots and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be best suited as a major project car or for salvage parts.",
